{"attribution":"Federal Emergency Management Agency, Ready.gov, Earthquakes, Simplified Chinese; no FEMA, DHS, or U.S. Government endorsement or affiliation is implied.","cases":[{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-001","input":"地震是由地表深处的岩石移动引起的突然、快速的地面震动，会导致火灾、海啸、山体滑坡或雪崩。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-001","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-002","input":"虽然可能在没有警告的情况下在任何地方发生，但是，地震风险较高的地区包括阿拉斯加、加州、夏威夷、俄勒冈、波多黎各、华盛顿和整个密西西比河谷。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-002","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-003","input":"为任何灾难做好防备的最佳时间是在发生之前。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-003","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-004","input":"与家人和同事练习如何在地震发生时保护自己。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-004","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-005","input":"制定应急计划：制定一个有州外联系人的家庭应急通信计划。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-005","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-006","input":"安排好走散了在哪里见面。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-006","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-007","input":"制作一个备灾用品包，含有够几天用的食物和用水、一个手电筒、一个灭火器和一个口哨。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-007","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-008","input":"做好防备可避免不必要的远足，在家中解决轻微的医疗问题，减轻紧急护理中心和医院的负担。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-008","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-009","input":"切记：并非每个人都能负担得起储备应对需要的必需品。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-009","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-010","input":"如果负担得起，应进行必要的购买并慢慢积累用品。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-010","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-011","input":"保护住房：固定好家中的重物，如书柜、冰箱、热水器、电视和墙上挂的物品。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-011","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-012","input":"将重物和易碎物放在低的架子上。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-012","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-013","input":"考虑改进住房，以解决在地震中可能导致倒塌的结构问题。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-013","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-014","input":"考虑购买地震保单。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-014","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-015","input":"标准的房主保险不包括地震损坏。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-015","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-016","input":"如在车中，应靠边停车。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-016","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-017","input":"放好驻车制动器。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-017","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-018","input":"如在床上，脸朝下，用枕头盖住头部和颈部。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-018","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-019","input":"如在户外，应远离建筑物。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-019","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-020","input":"如在室内，呆在里面，不要跑到外面，避开门口。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-020","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-021","input":"无论身在何处，都要双手双膝着地，抓住坚固的东西。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-021","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-022","input":"如果使用带座椅的轮椅或助行器，务必锁定轮子，保持就位，直到晃动停止。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-022","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-023","input":"用手臂盖住头部和颈部。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-023","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-024","input":"如果附近有坚固的桌子或书桌，爬到下面用作庇护所。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-024","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-025","input":"如果附近没有庇护所，爬到内墙旁边（远离窗户）。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-025","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-026","input":"如能不经过碎片更多的地方，可爬到更好的掩体处。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-026","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-027","input":"保持双膝着地或弯腰，护好重要器官。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-027","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-028","input":"如在桌子或书桌下面，用一只手扶好，准备好随之移动。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-028","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-029","input":"如果坐着且无法爬到在地，向前弯腰，用双手盖住头部和颈部。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-029","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-030","input":"地震后可能会出现严重的危险，例如，建筑物损坏、煤气和水管泄漏或电线掉落。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-030","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-031","input":"预期主震后会有余震。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-031","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-032","input":"如果感到余震，准备好爬下、盖住和扶好。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-032","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-033","input":"如在损坏的建筑物内，应到外面，迅速离开建筑物。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-033","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-034","input":"不要进入损坏的建筑物。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-034","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-035","input":"如果被困，发送短信或敲打水管或墙壁。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-035","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-036","input":"用衬衫捂住嘴部，保护好自己，不要大喊大叫，而要使用哨子。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-036","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-037","input":"如果所在地区可能发生海啸，在震动停止后应立即前往内陆或地势较高的地方。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-037","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-038","input":"避免接触洪水，因为水里可能有化学物质、污水和碎屑。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-038","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-039","input":"检查自己是否受伤，如果受过培训，可帮助他人。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-039","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-040","input":"了解如何在救援到来之前提供帮助。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-040","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-041","input":"如因生病或受伤而需就医，联系医护人员获取说明。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-041","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-042","input":"安全后，留意当地新闻报道，通过电池供电的收音机、电视、社交媒体或手机短信警示获取紧急情况信息和说明。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-042","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-043","input":"使用短信进行交流，因为可能比电话更可靠。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-043","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-044","input":"穿好防护服，包括长袖衬衫，长裤，工作手套和坚固的厚底鞋。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-044","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-045","input":"切勿尝试自行清除沉重的碎屑。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-045","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-046","input":"清洁霉菌或其他碎屑时，应戴上合适的面罩。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-046","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-047","input":"如患哮喘和其他肺部疾病和/或免疫抑制，则不应进入室内有可以看到或闻到漏水或霉菌生长的建筑物。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-047","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1/sentence-048","input":"儿童不应参加灾后清理工作。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/earthquakes","source_case_id":"sentence-048","split":"article"}}],"converter_output_used":false,"dataset":"blind-v2","id":"ready-gov-earthquakes-zh-hans-v1","input_only":true,"license":"U.S. Public Domain","modification_notice":"Extracted only complete Simplified Chinese paragraph and list-item sentences from the checksum-pinned Ready.gov main element, removed navigation, images, external resources, phone/URL instructions, page furniture, and exact duplicates, and added input-only provenance; no expected text or converter output was used.","purpose":"candidate_source_pilot","review_policy":"domain_and_risk_must_be_assigned_from_input_only","source_class":"public_domain","stats":{"by_split":{"article":48},"eligible_pending_review":48,"exclusions":{},"raw_cases":48},"upstream_revision":"Ready.gov Simplified Chinese Earthquakes; page last updated 2025-10-22; retrieved HTML SHA-256: d060c9b0cf07a88264c2288380fda65b662fd342392446918919a2059a44dfea","version":1}
